QuestData.Title: Elder Atuik and Kamagua
QuestData.Description: <Orfus bundles up the clues you brought him.>$B$BMy people are bitterly entrenched in a war with the Northsea Freebooters. If any tuskarr could help us in our quest to right the wrongs of the pirates, it will be Elder Atuik of Kamagua. You must take these clues to him at once.$B$BTo get to Kamagua you must take the Ancient Lift, behind me. Take the lift directly to Kamagua and find Elder Atuik.
QuestData.LogDescription: Orfus of Kamagua in the Howling Fjord wants you to deliver Orfus's Bundle to Elder Atuik at Kamagua.
QuestData.RewardText: Orfus is a good tuskarr - one of our strongest warriors. I knew he would not let us down.$B$BAllow me to see what it is that you have brought.
